column5: We are heading up to Little Minniss Lake for a weeks worth of fishing in July. Anyone who has been there and can give us some tips? We would appreciate it.

[font size="1" color="#FF0000"]LAST EDITED ON Feb-09-01 AT 05:02AM (CST)[/font][p]Do you mean Pickerel Arm Camps? If so, I can tell you everything you want to know. This one's located on Lake Minnataki.
